overview: TUSHY.com brings you girls who like doubling their pleasure with MY DP. This series is dedicated to insatiable women who need that extra pressure. Featured cover girl Nicole Doshi is a businesswoman who wants a bonus out of this deal, and shes not settling for anything less than a twofer. Stefany Kyler, Gia Derza, and Venera Maxima are all up for taking on a tag-team. Sense-shattering stories, breathtaking production values, and overwhelming action: TUSHY.com knows youll get your fill with MY DP.
title: My DP 5
